| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5667 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dd1c45c7-d5ac-59ee-bde5-2653c3c0bcb9"
